    <title>一台电脑部署两hexo</title>
    <link href="/2023/02/03/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%A4hexo/"/>
    <url>/2023/02/03/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%A4hexo/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>当部署好第一个hexo后按，以下方法部署第二个hexo</p><h3 id="一、创建第二个密钥"><a href="#一、创建第二个密钥" class="headerlink" title="一、创建第二个密钥"></a>一、创建第二个密钥</h3><p>CMD命令进入.ssh文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-8yl7i2ldqsjiqs"></i><span>bash</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-8yl7i2ldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ./.ssh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>然后创建密钥，创建密钥有2种方法：</p><h6 id="密钥方法一："><a href="#密钥方法一：" class="headerlink" title="密钥方法一："></a>密钥方法一：</h6><figure class="highlight awk"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-l0e566ldqsjiqs"></i><span>awk</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-l0e566ldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><span class="hljs-comment"># 这种方法创建的密钥名字默认的，默认是id_rsa</span><br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;这里是你的github邮箱&quot;</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><h6 id="密钥方法二："><a href="#密钥方法二：" class="headerlink" title="密钥方法二："></a>密钥方法二：</h6><figure class="highlight awk"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-enn4f6ldqsjiqs"></i><span>awk</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-enn4f6ldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><span class="hljs-comment"># 这种方法可以指定密钥文件名称</span><br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -f ~.<span class="hljs-regexp">/.ssh/</span>这里是密钥名称 -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;这里是github邮箱&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>第二个密钥名称要记住，后面配置config文件需要。</p><h3 id="二、Github添加SSH-keys"><a href="#二、Github添加SSH-keys" class="headerlink" title="二、Github添加SSH keys"></a>二、Github添加SSH keys</h3><p>登陆Github账号，点右上角头像-<strong>settings</strong>,在左边导航点<strong>SSH and GPG keys</strong>-<strong>New SSH key</strong></p><p><strong>title</strong>: 随便填写</p><p><strong>key type</strong>: 默认</p><p><strong>key</strong>: 把第二个密钥.pub文件里面的内容粘贴进去</p><h3 id="三、创建并配置config文件"><a href="#三、创建并配置config文件" class="headerlink" title="三、创建并配置config文件"></a>三、创建并配置config文件</h3><p>CMD进入.ssh文件夹：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-3m2gawldqsjiqs"></i><span>bash</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-3m2gawldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ./.ssh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>进入.ssh文件夹后输入：<code>touch config</code> 创建config文件(注意没后缀)</p><p>用记事本打开config，然后按下方配置：</p><figure class="highlight crmsh"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-eig83kldqsjiqs"></i><span>crmsh</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-eig83kldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">Host github.com<br>HostName github.com<br><span class="hljs-keyword">User</span> <span class="hljs-title">git</span><br>IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa <span class="hljs-comment"># id_rsa是第一个hexo的密钥名称（创建如果没指定名称默认这个），</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#第二个新账号，#&quot;xxxxxx&quot;为前缀名，可以任意设置，要记住，后面配置hexo的config文件需要用到</span><br>Host xxxxxx.github.com<br>HostName github.com<br><span class="hljs-keyword">User</span> <span class="hljs-title">git</span><br>IdentityFile ~/.ssh/这里是第二个密钥的名称<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><h3 id="四、添加添加新的密钥到SSH-agent中"><a href="#四、添加添加新的密钥到SSH-agent中" class="headerlink" title="四、添加添加新的密钥到SSH agent中"></a>四、添加添加新的密钥到SSH agent中</h3><p>命令进入.ssh文件夹，输入以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-vjgp9ildqsjiqs"></i><span>mipsasm</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-vjgp9ildqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mipsasm">ssh-agent <span class="hljs-keyword">bash</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword"></span>ssh-agent -D<br>ssh-<span class="hljs-keyword">add </span>这里是第一个密钥名称 <span class="hljs-comment">#一般默认是id_rsa</span><br>ssh-<span class="hljs-keyword">add </span>这里是第二个密钥名称<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>添加好后需要验证依次执行以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight angelscript"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-ngvd75ldqsjiqs"></i><span>angelscript</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-ngvd75ldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs angelscript">ssh -T <span class="hljs-symbol">git@</span>github.com<br>ssh- T <span class="hljs-symbol">git@</span>第二个密钥名称.github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>如果返回以下信息表示配置成功</p><div class="note note-success">            <p>Hi 你的用户名! You’ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</p>          </div><h3 id="五、单独设置第二个hexo的用户名和邮箱"><a href="#五、单独设置第二个hexo的用户名和邮箱" class="headerlink" title="五、单独设置第二个hexo的用户名和邮箱"></a>五、单独设置第二个hexo的用户名和邮箱</h3><p>在第二个hexo目录下找到**.deploy_git<strong>文件夹，进入后鼠标右键空白出打开</strong>Git Bash Here**。</p><p>输入以下命令设置用户名和邮箱：</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-hgra4aldqsjiqs"></i><span>pgsql</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-hgra4aldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">git config <span class="hljs-keyword">user</span>.name &quot;你Git的用户名&quot;<br>git config <span class="hljs-keyword">user</span>.email &quot;你Git的邮箱&quot;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>如果找不到.deploy_git文件夹，可以在第二hexo目录下打开cmd命令或者git bash her，输入命令：</p><figure class="highlight nginx"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-frsxb3ldqsjiqs"></i><span>nginx</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-frsxb3ldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo</span> g -d <span class="hljs-comment"># 这个命令中g是hexo生成静态页面，-d是生成后部署到</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><h3 id="六、修改hexo-config文件"><a href="#六、修改hexo-config文件" class="headerlink" title="六、修改hexo config文件"></a>六、修改hexo config文件</h3><p>在第二个hexo根目录下找到**.config_yml<strong>文件，用记事本打开，找到</strong>deploy**，按下面的修改。</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-jpcg65ldqsjiqs"></i><span>stylus</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-jpcg65ldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repository: git@这里填第三步HOST里面你修改的名称<span class="hljs-selector-class">.github</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.com</span>:这里填你github用户名/这里贴你github用户名<span class="hljs-selector-class">.github</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.io</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.git</span><br>  branch: main<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>保存后，CMD命令或者git bash 中输入</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><i class="iconfont icon-xiangxiajiantou" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-gxcw0pldqsjiqs"></i><span>ebnf</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-gxcw0pldqsjiqs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo g -d</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>就可以把本地的部署到git上了，在浏览器中输入：git用户名.github.io ，就可以看到你的hexo博客。</p>]]></content>
    
    
